{"id":245444,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-张家港访民陈秀琴因上访被企业停缴保险/","date":"2012-08-07T11:31:07Z","modified":"2012-08-07T11:31:07Z","title":"维权网 | 张家港访民陈秀琴因上访被企业停缴保险（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张成报道）陈秀琴是江苏省张家港市南丰镇永联村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>组</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>号村民，</span><span>本来靠种田谋生。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2002</span><span>年土地被吴家永钢集团霸占建厂房，陈秀琴就开小店谋生，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年又遭殴打和非法强拆后，陈秀琴被迫到吴家集团上班。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<pre><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>月，陈秀琴交了<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>万多元买职工城镇社会保险。后来因为自己遭强拆后没有得到任何补偿和安置，陈秀琴两次请假去北京上访，被抓回后遭吴家集团停止工作至今，城镇社会保险和医疗保险也停了。</pre>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陈秀琴于今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日退休，陈秀琴发短信给村委书记吴惠芳和镇长金俊龙，质问自己因为被停工，职工城镇社会保险和医疗保险也遭到停止，需要补缴</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>万元，对方不理不睬。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陈秀琴认为，自己因为土地被强征，房屋遭到强拆，为了依法维护自己的权益上访，不料又遭到停发工资、无法缴纳保险等侵害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>联系电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13862231862 </span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-7fc3ePJdfoc/UCDso2-R1cI/AAAAAAAALD4/cBdsuoSe4ZI/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-7fc3ePJdfoc/UCDso2-R1cI/AAAAAAAALD4/cBdsuoSe4ZI/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5977166014044541059?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.co